1952;;Hellgate;;American;;Charles Warren;;Sterling Hayden, Joan Leslie;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hellgate_(1952_film);;Hellgate Prison is an aptly named facility in the desert where the worst criminals are sent. Hanley, a veterinarian and former Civil War soldier, is falsely accused and convicted of a crime. He is sentenced to this hellish place.<br><br>He immediately gets on the wrong side of Voorhees, a vicious guard, and Redfield, a mean convict. Hanley will need to fight his way out, particularly when the prisoners are afflicted with an epidemic of a spreading plague.